      "content": "i've talked to people. i've done the therapy, the doctors, the everything. it doesn't fix the fact that i'm just exhausted to my core. it feels like i've been running a race for years and i finally just hit a wall. i just want everything to stop. why does everyone keep trying to push me to \"keep going\" when there isn't even anything left to go toward?",
